author: stsp
msg: [Note from the future: This revision was reverted in r36147]
Make it possible for external merge tools to abort the merge
by exiting with an exit code other than 0 or 1.
and return an error if it is not 0 and not 1.
(svn_io_wait_for_cmd): Better document under what conditions callers
can expect to retrieve the exit code of the child process.

msg: * www/hacking.html: clarify some change management guidelines for releases.

author: hwright
msg: Make dead certain svnmerge-migrate-history.py can't create mergeinfo
with overlapping or unordered rangelists.  Subversion <= 1.5.5 will
error out if it tries to parse this mergeinfo, see issue #3302.

author: hwright
msg: libsvn_ra_serf: Following RFC2617, verify authentication header tokens
Enables using serf from behind Microsoft ISA proxy servers.
